{"tid":1589852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"To ALL FIRST AIDER","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:42:02.000Z","uid":232797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42c7041ce7c9e52d258b88e2e36a1fd5f0362d88","tid":1589852,"uid":232797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"《鋼鋸嶺》上的美軍醫療兵，因為宗教信念不會拿武器殺人，但他會從日軍槍下搶回受傷的同袍。更重要的，是他不會傻到以為「救人是天職」而走去為敵人包紥止血，不會在美軍進攻日軍時衝出來攔住叫「夠啦夠啦唔好再打」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔撚想再見到左膠</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">見一個打一個</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5VnOG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5VnOG1.jpg&h=3ff11b1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dccbe256005f6f4a6859a522624779574737063","tid":1589852,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"}]}